des:
- Download our "Sleek Life" app from Google Play or iOS App Store;
- Launch the app and register a new account (or login if you’ve already registered it);
- Turn on Sleek Life devices and connect them with “Sleek Life” app;
- IMPORTANT: You can rename the devices with“Sleek Life” app;
 So if you rename a smart bulb “my living room light”, then Echo will get that same name after discovering the devices
- Download Amazon "Alexa" app from Amazon Market, Google Play or iOS App Store, and connect Echo with "Alexa" app;
- Search the Alexa Skills directory for "Sleek Life";
- Click Enable skill of "Sleek Life", then input your account username, password and region on the linked page;
- Talk to Echo "“Alexa,discover devices.”. Wait till Echo says "Discovery is completed";
- Now all the setup is done. Try to talk to Echo to control your devices.

Alexa, turn on my living room light
Alexa, turn off my living room light
Alexa, dim my living room light
